# Wesley Bomar

## Website UI Technology Architect Communications, Media, and Design

Email: **[wbomar@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:wbomar@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Wesley joined TACC in October 2019. He is involved in website maintenance and development, and the identification and realization of new opportunities to improve user experience and developer workflow. Prior to joining TACC, he worked ten years in private industry closely with designers and engineers on user-centric website and web application development and architecture.

### Current Projects

* [TACC/tup-ui](https://github.com/TACC/tup-ui)
* [TACC/Core-CMS](https://github.com/TACC/Core-CMS)
* [TACC/Core-Styles](https://github.com/TACC/Core-Styles)
* [TACC/TACC-Docs](https://github.com/TACC/TACC-Docs)
* [DesignSafe-CI/DS-User-Guide](https://github.com/DesignSafe-CI/DS-User-Guide)